Dashboard: Employee Wage Growth:

Created another Dashboard Employee Wage Growth. Drag and drop Hourly wages for each company, Region wise hourly wages and Map.

Drag and drop all charts and filtered with each other.

Go to Dashboard and select Action 

Click on Add Action

click filter then ok

Give name of filter and then check 3 selected charts. Click on Menu and then keep the rest as it is and then click ok 

after that click anywhere and will get result. 


This Is Final Dashboard
